ğŸš€ How to Use
Option 1: Live Demo
Simply open the index.html file in any modern web browser. No installation or dependencies required!

Option 2: Deploy Online
Upload all files to your web server

Access via browser

No backend required - works entirely in the browser

ğŸ“‹ Usage Guide
1. Generate Username QR Code
Select the Username tab

Enter your Telegram username (without @ symbol)

Click "Generate Username QR"

Download or share the QR code

2. Generate Direct Link QR Code
Select the Direct Link tab

Paste any Telegram link:

Profile: https://t.me/username

Group: https://t.me/joinchat/xxxxx

Channel: https://t.me/channelname

Bot: https://t.me/botname

Select link type (auto-detected)

Generate QR code

3. Generate Message QR Code
Select the Message tab

Enter username or chat ID

Add optional pre-filled message

Generate QR that opens chat with message

